title: T207 Blank Back Livingston and Lennox
author: Luke

posts.post_title: T207 Blank Back Livingston and Lennox
posts.post_content:
Offering up a couple of tough Blank Backs.  I'm not aware of any other Cleveland players existing with a Blank Back.  I also have a Needham, and I'm not aware of any other Cubs players with Blank Backs besides those two.  It's a little tough to tell from the pop reports, so there could definitely be cards I'm not aware of out there.  The Livingston is kind of cool in that PSA didn't notice that it's hand-cut and gave it a numerical grade

Livingston PSA 2 $1200

Lennox SGC A $850
Nice cards Luke ... unbelievable PSA gave that card a number though!!
